{"tid":1269563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咪撚去愛丁堡呀屌你老母","createTime":"2019-06-30T15:15:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T17:02:15.000Z","uid":33567,"like":86,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"de4a6e0a519ec1c4e9bd7b376ff35f21af073cf2","tid":1269563,"uid":33567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:15:07.000Z","msg":"匿埋一二角打飛機把撚呀，出得嚟就係要撼動政權<br />\n630金紫荊見。"},{"pid":"16842d82a3f82cdac0fd51b2f05745b3dbea93c9","tid":1269563,"uid":33567,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:20:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef742e325a1f13331dd53d3de10c95ebc225a107","tid":1269563,"uid":228493,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:24:13.000Z","msg":"黃之峰想係愛丁堡聽朝8點升黑旗 首先唔講其實我地要阻既 更加重要既 係0630果個升旗禮<br />\n<br />\n正題<br />\n黑旗係國際政治意識形態上面 的確係等於無政府主義 Anarchy<br />\n你唔鐘意游蕙禎係ok既 但係呢個係客觀事實<br />\n游蕙禎有手指尾 你都有手指尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無政府主義 國際社運而家主要係一班新左翼進步青年帶<br />\n極左 但唔係共產黨 更加唔係左膠 無政府主義者比起連登仔一定更勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單而言anarchy係以人民公社同革命工人取締政府官僚同資產階級既社會機能<br />\n外國好多都有antifa反法西斯既激烈抗爭團體<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>唔識真係唔好亂用 一來有國際傳媒見到 二來我地抗爭個意識形態光譜太散 黑旗絕對代表唔到群眾</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n比呢個大家參考下其他無政府主義旗幟既類型<br />\n利申 右膠 覺得全部都唔係好野留<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aBShp8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaBShp8L.png&h=58403908&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"308dbc91a873a22b1d0420995c0e94c190e938ec","tid":1269563,"uid":33567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:31:00.000Z","msg":"悼念/葬禮都會用黑旗"},{"pid":"941ceb35936c8342dd3f41976bc4b73654dfb53a","tid":1269563,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:50:05.000Z","msg":"阻你少少時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我見到好多post話71 係去示威遊行就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 各位 抗爭左成個月 聽日金紫荊廣場大好機會見到政府高官 點解仲要揀去示威遊行 你地只要行出黎企出黎就幫到啲義士 唔好個個話我唔衝 無人要你衝呀 我地要人數幫啲義士cover呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我求下你地聽日朝早出黎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oa6Vbqx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foa6Vbqx.jpg&h=7af281a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MLcAVSd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMLcAVSd.jpg&h=67b44608&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dyy8wqz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdyy8wqz.jpg&h=18391795&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ab5464c8c014b800e9a016227a7107c30d9f396","tid":1269563,"uid":81323,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:53:58.000Z","msg":"見到扯黑旗活動當堂笑撚左<br />\n又係搞埋嗰啲 x japan 活動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都畀人呃咗咁多年啦，仲去同佢哋玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由始至終71最有noise兼令全球關注嘅行動就只有扯唔到旗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284bff0b60858e32f86ad3a265e28f4d35af61f6","tid":1269563,"uid":268827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:55:03.000Z","msg":"唔明點解要搞愛丁堡"},{"pid":"8c7cbc16029176019d504318e964687864e537c8","tid":1269563,"uid":261169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3b028e31119ddcb335674c3e992fc82103265647","tid":1269563,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike